"They will.TaskbarThe most remarkable new feature of Windows 7, and the one that people will interact with most often, is the new taskbar"
"I've covered this in detail before, but for those new to the new appearance, I'll give a brief overview.The new taskbar melds the old Quick Launch toolbar with the traditional taskbar, providing a single place to both launch applications and switch between them"
