"Microsoft wants you to use the new Start menu, so by golly you're gonna use it.Explorer and Control PanelExplorer received quite a facelift in Vista, and Windows 7 Explorer refines the appearance a great deal (no more ugly blue-green toolbar), retaining good things like the clickable breadcrumb bar and ubiquitous search box.Unfortunately, Windows 7's Explorer also retains bad things, like the monumentally stupid Search window"
