"If vendors can sort out this mess and do their part, it'll be a worthy addition to the platform; but if nine times out of ten my devices won't have a Device Stage, I'm probably not going to bother the one time in ten that they do.Keyboardability and window managementOne of the things that has long annoyed me about Windows is that basic window management operations aren't keyboardable"
