"Sure, much of the interface remains the same, but Microsoft has completely overhauled key elements, starting with the Taskbar.The New TaskbarAfter 14 years of nothing more than cosmetic changes, Microsoftâ€™s redesign of the Taskbar combines the pure window organizing power of the classic Taskbar with the application-launching, multi-purpose convenience of Mac OS Xâ€™s Dock"
